snippet.title: FFXI Braver 200% Difficulty Diablos Battle, PLD, BRD, RDM SAM.
snippet.description:
A test battle to see if SAM is better at closing weaponskills than BRD.  It should be!

Best closing weaponskill damage to date!  Lazulai the SAM shines.
